{"title": "Song Celestial; Or, Bhagavad-G\u00eet\u00e2", "description": "This work is a unique rendering of the Bagavad Gita by a well known poet. It is faithful to the text and yet does not read like a translation.The Sanskrit original is written in the Anushtubh metre. It has been cast into flexible blank verse by Sir Arnold, changing into lyrical measures where the text itself similarly breaks. In his autobiography, Gandhi has called this work the book par excellence for the Knowledge of Truth and that it afforded him invaluable help in his moments of gloom. (Summary by Jothi)", "duration": 11762, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "221", "name": " Unknown"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/bhagavad-gita_1502_librivox/the_song_celestial_1502.jpg", "copyright_year": "1900", "genres": ["Epics"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Jothi Tharavant"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Jothi Tharavant"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "pattymarie"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Preface", "readers": [9216], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bhagavad-gita_1502_librivox/songcelestialorbhagavadgita_00__64kb.mp3", "duration": 392}, {"section": 1, "title": "Chapter 1 -  The Book of the Distress of Arjuna", "readers": [9216], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bhagavad-gita_1502_librivox/songcelestialorbhagavadgita_01__64kb.mp3", "duration": 569}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter 2 - The Book of Doctrines", "readers": [9216], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bhagavad-gita_1502_librivox/songcelestialorbhagavadgita_02__64kb.mp3", "duration": 1097}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter 3 - The Book of Virtue in Work", "readers": [9216], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bhagavad-gita_1502_librivox/songcelestialorbhagavadgita_03__64kb.mp3", "duration": 572}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter 4 - The Book of the Religion of Knowledge", "readers": [9216], "path":